<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="half-adv">half <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /hɑːf/    美 /hæf/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>一半地；部分地：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He looks <strong>half asleep</strong>.
他看上去半睡半醒。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He was half dead with tiredness. 
他累得半死。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don't leave the work half done.
工作不要半途而废。</p></div></div>